warehouse

Class Master

  • java.lang.Object
    • warehouse.Master

  • public class Master
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Ted Herman The Master class runs the simulated warehouse. It creates initial instances of Floor, Robot, Inventory, Orders, Belt, and Vizualizer. It has a method to generate "tick" events to all the Tickable components, and it should also provide a scheduled Event service (not yet coded).
